Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.83,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Akhirnya kau tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa-apaan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pilih ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Bukankah Kaoru mau yang lingkaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pilih yang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ini bagus.\NKatanya dia mau yang paling manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.10,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membawanya merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.48,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kempeskan dan lipat saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:33.27,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kasihan salamander raksasa ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.02,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah terpikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:40.11,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah Kaoru mendapat teman
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk berenang bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:42.49,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak ingat apa pun\Nsoal menjadi Nonuki-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya aku ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.84,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa aku lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.63,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi belakangan ini
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mulai teringat sedikit-sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.09,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terutama soal mengabulkan permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar merasa\Nbisa mengabulkan permintaan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sombong sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan apa pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, coba saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.49,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski sekarang kita tahu soal Nonuki-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.95,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita masih belum tahu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cara menangani noda-noda ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:30.29,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus bertindak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Desa dan kotanya…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu sketsa itu untuk apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertanyaannya justru makin banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yoshiki, lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ia menari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ia sudah terbiasa denganmu?\N- Mince!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.27,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:58.23,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ia cuma menyukaiku saat kubawakan camilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.11,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka ia sekuat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duduk berpikir di sini selamanya\Ntak ada gunanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau ke pantai sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau melihatnya sekali saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini… Gila.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luas sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Laut memang keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.90,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat, sepatuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo masuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Nanti celanamu basah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barusan, aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.45,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah menepati janji
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melihat laut bersama, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.70,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran Asako, Maki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Yuki sedang apa sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu mereka marah\Nkarena kita bolos konser paduan suara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bernyanyi bersama mereka\Npasti menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu liriknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Menuju masa depan, detak di jantungku."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat menyentuh hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan sunyi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau menyanyi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Terus jalani hidup itu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Liriknya salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dengan jelas{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Terus bicara seperti biasa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Meski bunga masa lalu{\i0}\N{\i1}Tak bisa kembali lagi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Menuju masa depan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Detak di jantungku ini{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sekarang…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum meninggal,\NHikaru membuat permintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku tak mau membuat orang lain sedih."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku tak mau Yoshiki sendirian."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengabulkannya.\NItu sebabnya aku di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permintaan Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tapi sepertinya aku\Ntak bisa mengabulkannya sampai akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau kembali ke gunung.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini aku terus menyerangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa itu sebabnya\Ndiriku yang asli terus muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mengisi\Nbagian diriku yang kosong,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku ingin melahap jiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia tak mungkin mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya aku memang makhluk seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah membunuh banyak orang,\Nmungkin aku akan mulai membunuh lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak mau membunuhmu, Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku kembali ke gunung,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setidaknya semuanya akan damai\Nselama sisa hidupmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Tidak! Tidak boleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu untuk apa kita meneliti semua itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monsternya pergi,\Nkau menerima kematian Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terus maju menjalani kehidupan normal\Ndan hidup bahagia selama…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau berada di sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Bagaimana dengan "setengah" dirimu\Nyang kau berikan kepadaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau abadi, 'kan? Kau bisa\Nmembuang tubuh itu kapan pun kau mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat? Kita masih belum tahu\Nbagaimana cara kerjanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terima rencana gegabah begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi cuma itu\Nrencana yang kita punya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah apa itu benar, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa bodoh! Kau tak perlu\Nmelakukan hal yang benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak perlu memedulikan hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanan favorit Hikaru adalah semangka,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku suka es krim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih suka Papicco\Ndaripada Gachi Gachi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga suka kucing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka menonton film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua film yang kutonton\Ntak ada yang membosankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hikaru benci belajar, tapi aku suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku tidak pandai belajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lalu apa lagi?\N- Hentikan, kumohon…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada bersamamu\Nsangat menyenangkan, Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bagimu, mungkin aku cuma pengganti Hikaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi meski aku seperti ini,{\i0}\N{\i1}kau memberikanku begitu banyak hal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat menyayangimu, Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bukan secara romantis\Natau sebagai teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa itu berbeda dari emosi apa pun\Nyang dirasakan manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tetap saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu perasaanku yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan sebagai Hikaru,\Ntapi sebagai monster, diriku yang asli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kau tak boleh menjadi normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Rasanya sesak…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku selalu menyembunyikan{\i0}\N{\i1}diriku sebenarnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu sebabnya aku mau dia diselamatkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Karena ada bersamamu juga menyelamatkanku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Selama ini, aku cuma bersikap egois.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Demi Hikaru? Demi desa?{\i0}\N{\i1}Aku cuma melempar tanggung jawab.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku putus asa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pada akhirnya, ini semua kulakukan{\i0}\N{\i1}demi diriku sendiri.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas segalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan pengganti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.23,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cuma menyerah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.35,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyuruhku terus maju?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang sudah terlambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang salah dengan pilihan {\i1}Hikaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau sadar seberapa keras\Naku berjuang untukmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia monster sungguhan.\NTidak seperti diriku…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir aku mau menerima ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak mau pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monsternya akan pergi,\Nlalu kami hidup bahagia selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu semua ini untuk apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, sebaiknya kau berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau kembali ke gunung!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti berkata egois seperti itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus menyingkirkanku,\Nmenyingkirkan monster ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pilihan terbaik untukmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak perlu normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku cuma bersikap egois…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu menyembunyikan diriku\Nagar tak tahu diriku yang sebenarnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Hikaru…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli meski kau pembunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Hikaru!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:11.31,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan pengganti Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau kau menghilang dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bajingan jahat dan egois.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu perasaanmu yang sebenarnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baru mengatakannya sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:47.80,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salamander raksasanya!\NItu mengapung sampai ke sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.65,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tak membawanya pulang,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaoru akan menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak butuh itu.\NBiarkan mengapung sampai jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:28.43,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kau jauh lebih kekanakan dariku.
